rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0010
rows.name: Looks like our man.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0020
rows.name: Are you Ted?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0030
rows.name: Hey, you're Elma's team![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0040
rows.name: What are you doing here?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0050
rows.name: We came looking for you, at Eric's request.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0060
rows.name: Captain sent you...?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0070
rows.name: I'm sorry.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0080
rows.name: You came out here for me? You didn't have to.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0090
rows.name: Let me be straight.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0100
rows.name: The plan hasn't changed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0110
rows.name: Will you return to NLA?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0130
rows.name: Here's where we are.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0140
rows.name: Your being here right now is dereliction of duty.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0150
rows.name: I won't lie. We could take you into custody.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0160
rows.name: ...Look, I can't get on board with it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0170
rows.name: Because we're not bringing plants and animals?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0180
rows.name: Exactly.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0190
rows.name: You must realize why. The logistical hurdles alone.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0200
rows.name: Sure.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0210
rows.name: And yet...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0220
rows.name: they're what nurtured this planet.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0230
rows.name: Since way, way before we arrived.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0240
rows.name: And just because we showed up,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0250
rows.name: the whole world's...just gonna disappear like that.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0260
rows.name: If I can't stop it, I'd rather go with them...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_JNK0010
rows.name: Respect

rows.label: xs32290100_SEL0010
rows.name: Agree that it might be fitting.

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0270
rows.name:
I think what you're saying is right,
and it deserves attention.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0280
rows.name: But...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0290
rows.name: How do I put this...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0300
rows.name:
Just don't forget there's people looking out for you.
You got that, Ted?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_JNK0020
rows.name: Reason

rows.label: xs32290100_SEL0020
rows.name: Tell him to think carefully.

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0310
rows.name: Right.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0320
rows.name: You have to follow your own conscience, no question.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0330
rows.name: We will respect your decision.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0340
rows.name: But...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0350
rows.name:
You need to remember that by doing this,
you'll be forcing people to leave you behind.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0360
rows.name: [ST:undisp ]...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0370
rows.name:
Well, I'm sure you've had time to consider it
from all angles by now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0380
rows.name: I'm sorry.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0390
rows.name: I know what I'm doing is pointless, but still...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0400
rows.name: What if friend took along jam-netic information?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0410
rows.name:
The genetic information of the
plants and animals of Mira...?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0420
rows.name: Like Tatsu say![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0430
rows.name: I don't think there's any rule against it...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0440
rows.name: Clever...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0450
rows.name: You want to emulate the Earthlife Colonization Project,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0460
rows.name:
by preserving the genetic information of
Mira's flora and fauna.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0470
rows.name: Tatsu knew Elma would get it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0480
rows.name: That what Tatsu said![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0490
rows.name: Tatsu happy friend pick up what Tatsu lay down![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0500
rows.name: Whew. That's some good thinking, for a Nopon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0510
rows.name: Friend could have left off that last part![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0520
rows.name:
Our time is limited, though.
We won't be able to capture all of it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0530
rows.name: Verdict?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0540
rows.name: We'll help you however we can![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0550
rows.name: Yes, I'm all for.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0560
rows.name:
If we can bring even a small memento of Mira's
existence to the next universe we live in...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0570
rows.name: I want to make it happen.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0580
rows.name:
I can gather the data we need from Noctilum.
Can you do the other continents?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0590
rows.name: Of course.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0600
rows.name:
I've sent you the coordinates for a spot in
Primordia that'll make for good data.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0610
rows.name: Best of luck.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32290100_MSG0620
rows.name: Let's move.[ST:wait ]
